Purpose: Manage users and their display names

Actions:
- register({ name }) -> { user } | { error }
- updateName({ user, newName }) -> { user } | { error }

Queries:
- _getById({ user }) -> [{ user, name }]
- _getByName({ name }) -> [{ user }]
- _getAllUsers() -> [{ user, name }]

State (MongoDB):
- users: { user, name }

